data.description: Welcome to this absolute stunning home in the great Townhomes at Lorson Ranch. The meticulously well maintained house is located on a large beautiful corner lot with infinite possibilities. This move in ready Townhome styled is sitting in one of the desirable neighborhoods in Colorado Springs with straight views to the mountains. This gorgeous 3 bedroom/ 3 bathroom home presents a great open space floor plan with ton of natural lights as you walk in. Enjoy the gourmet kitchen that offers plenty of storage space with granite countertops, new backsplash, new appliance and magnificent dining room. Enjoy the spacious living room with the double paned windows that offers plenty of bright natural light and enjoy the walk out deck paradise with new stamped concrete and new fence for more privacy and much more entertaining and outdoors! The upper level presents 3 sizable bedrooms, The primary suite offers 5 piece bathroom with soaking tub, huge walk-in closet and new faucets. Two more bedrooms to enjoy with separate closets and full updated bathroom. The property is minutes away from Manitou Springs, hiking and biking trails, parks and shopping centers. The property has the obvious quality and pride of ownership you are looking for. Hurry!!
